   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Local Cooperation Fund (LCF) in Tanzania</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Makuya Festival is an exciting celebration of the traditional performing arts and culture of Mtwara Region in Tanzania.The Centre for African Development through Economics and the Arts (ADEA) is organising this festival. Objectives of the activities are: 1) to promote, preserve and perpetuate the traditional performing arts of Mtwara region 2) to document the cultural, traditional and historic knowledge of the elders before their generation passes 3)  to reconnect the younger generation of Tanzania to their rich heritage and to expose this cultural richness to international visitors.
Funds will be used for festival preparations and support interviews with the elderss to learn learn of their heritage as well as documenting through recordings and photographs items of traditional life.</narrative>
  </description>
